Wow, what a pleasant surprise! This recipe was very good. I have never made (or wanted to make) a dish that included anchovy's. No one knew they were in this dish. It is salty and high in flavor, so make sure you pair it appropriately. DON'T NOT MAKE THIS BECAUSE OF THE ANCHOVY'S!!!

