Rating: 4
This was a wonderful recipe! It was very flavorful. We added onion to the tomato mixture and used a mixture of Munster and Feta cheese to give it a different taste. We were in a hurry, so we put the peppers in the microwave for 3 or 4 minutes first, then cooked it in the oven for 20 min. or so.

